{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"dc67e5e72d","title":"致刘伯承、邓小平等电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4e826ea95b","index":0,"year":1947,"month":10,"day":12,"articleId":"dc67e5e72d"}],"tags":[{"id":"5bd9678625","name":"邓小平","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji23","name":"毛泽东全集第23卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji23.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji23":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2bf0334264","type":"paragraph","text":"致刘伯承、邓小平等电”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"dc67e5e72d"},{"id":"faf6b63bde","type":"paragraph","text":"（1947年10月12日）自你们进到鄂豫皖边区并立住脚跟，配合陈、菜在准河以北陈、谢在豫西、陕南，彭、张在西北，许、谭在山东，我军已完成了南线第二年作战的战略展开，并打了许多胜仗，追使南线诸敌分散应付，处于被动，创造了我军在今后大量开敌的条件。尚望各同志在刘、邓正确领导下，继续努力，团结全党全军，克服困难，完成伟大战略任务[1]这是毛泽东为中共中央起草的致刘伯承、邓小平并转各纵队各旅电的主要内容。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"dc67e5e72d"}],"page":{"id":"64e3529cf4","publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"dc67e5e72d","start":361,"end":361}}}},"__N_SSG":true}